setReceiver.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the caller has the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
   ├─ when the new receiver is the same value as the old receiver
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the new receiver is not the same value as the old receiver
      ├─ it should set the new receiver
      └─ it should emit a ReceiverSet event
